to come tonight, okay?

16:44.837 --> 16:47.089
Just stay home.

16:47.172 --> 16:48.716
{\an5}-Jasmine, that's not
what I meant...
-No, I think...

16:48.799 --> 16:49.925
I think that's best.

16:50.008 --> 16:51.927
Don't come. Just stay.

16:52.010 --> 16:54.054
It's fine.

16:54.138 --> 16:58.142
