having you there anyways.

16:59.685 --> 17:01.437
Judgmental ass.

17:01.520 --> 17:02.813
-Okay.
<i>-(cheering, applause)</i>

17:02.896 --> 17:04.440
{\an8}<i>ANNOUNCER:</i>
Ovation,

17:04.522 --> 17:06.900
{\an8}<i>your host J.J. Malloy.</i>

