{\an8}<i>Brought to you</i>
<i>by Mr. Diggle's Ice Cream,</i>

17:10.487 --> 17:12.281
{\an8}<i>It's so good you'll die for it.</i>

17:12.364 --> 17:15.451
-Did you miss me? (laughs)
-(cheering)

17:15.534 --> 17:18.619
{\an8}It's the finals
on The Big Ovation.

17:18.704 --> 17:21.165
{\an8}You know, most of the stars
that you can see from Earth

17:21.248 --> 17:23.959
{\an8}died out millions of years ago.

17:24.041 --> 17:26.336
But tonight, with your applause,
we're gonna make

17:26.420 --> 17:30.299
one of these three young people
a brand-new star.

17:30.382 --> 17:32.968
I'm J.J. Malloy, and this...

17:33.051 --> 17:35.179
(drumroll)

17:35.262 --> 17:37.389
...is <i> Ovation.</i>

17:37.473 --> 17:39.099
(cheering, applause)

17:41.518 --> 17:43.520
(guitar playing)

17:51.195 --> 17:54.448
-(applause)
-♪<i> She dances for me</i> ♪

17:54.531 --> 17:56.492
♪<i> All that is she</i> ♪

17:56.575 --> 17:59.828
♪<i> I long to be</i> ♪

17:59.912 --> 18:01.997
(mutters)

18:02.080 --> 18:03.540
-Sorry.
-(applause continues)

18:03.624 --> 18:05.667
(guitar playing)

18:05.751 --> 18:07.961
♪<i> They silence her voice</i> ♪

18:08.045 --> 18:09.546
♪<i> But I hear her sway</i> ♪

18:14.927 --> 18:18.347
♪<i> Within the sea</i>
<i>of their shame...</i> ♪

18:20.140 --> 18:22.184
(clears throat)

18:22.267 --> 18:23.519
-(applause continues)
-(exhales) Sorry.

18:23.602 --> 18:24.520
(chuckles)

18:24.603 --> 18:27.272
(applause, cheering)

18:36.907 --> 18:39.618
(speaking indistinctly)

19:00.013 --> 19:01.348
(laughs):
Whoa!

19:01.431 --> 19:03.350
(echoing):
Ladies and gentlemen,

19:03.433 --> 19:09.106
Jasmine Delancey
