20:28.727 --> 20:30.729
(cheering, applause)

20:34.399 --> 20:38.028
{\an5}ZARA:
That's right.
It's the winner of <i> Ovation!</i>

20:38.111 --> 20:39.488
(mimics crowd roar)

20:39.571 --> 20:41.490
ZARA:
You see them?

20:41.573 --> 20:45.118
{\an5}-They've been out there
all night.
-Mm-hmm.

20:45.202 --> 20:47.829
Hey. Peace offering.

20:47.913 --> 20:50.165
I'm really sorry
I missed it last night.

20:50.249 --> 20:51.833
Clearly, you were amazing.

20:51.917 --> 20:54.544
Yeah, no, I wasn't.

20:54.628 --> 20:56.129
I was actually pretty awful.

20:56.213 --> 20:59.549
-No.
-I <i> was,</i> Z. I-I sang off-key,

20:59.633 --> 21:02.469
I forgot the frickin' chords,
and-and yet they clapped.

21:02.552 --> 21:05.013
