That man's got perfect pitch.

21:05.097 --> 21:09.309
Well, you must have done good,
'cause you won, right?

21:09.393 --> 21:12.187
(faint cheering, applause)

21:12.270 --> 21:14.481
Okay, I'm gonna say something,

21:14.564 --> 21:17.317
and it's gonna sound
like I'm crazy.

21:17.401 --> 21:19.695
I'm aware of that. Um...

21:19.778 --> 21:22.197
But I just need you
to stay open, you know,

21:22.280 --> 21:24.032
and not give me any of that,

21:24.116 --> 21:26.284
"Well, this is scientifically
impossible" bullshit

21:26.368 --> 21:28.495
-that you like to say.
-Okay.

21:28.578 --> 21:31.540
Fiji gave me this coin
right before she died,

21:31.623 --> 21:34.835
and ever since then...
I don't know, man.

21:34.918 --> 21:37.170
I-I-I-I, I mean, like,

21:37.254 --> 21:40.215
people listen to me.
They hear me.

21:40.298 --> 21:43.927
And even, like, I'm wondering,
you know, is it this coin?

21:44.011 --> 21:45.887
Is there something
in this coin that's, like,

21:45.971 --> 21:46.888
