22:02.654 --> 22:03.947
that's making all this happen?

22:04.990 --> 22:07.534
Yeah. No, I mean...

22:07.617 --> 22:09.369
it actually makes
a lot of sense.

22:09.453 --> 22:10.954
Yeah, right?

22:11.038 --> 22:13.457
Yeah, like, why would
all these people

22:13.540 --> 22:16.209
be clapping for someone
who just won

22:16.293 --> 22:18.086
the world's biggest
singing competition?

22:18.170 --> 22:21.548
Yeah, no, why, why?
Why would they like that?

22:21.631 --> 22:24.342
