underwear at the World Series?

22:34.853 --> 22:36.313
'Cause that is nasty.

22:36.396 --> 22:39.816
No, girl, they like <i> you,</i> okay?

22:39.900 --> 22:42.444
And that is why
they're clapping.

22:42.527 --> 22:44.488
-Look, look, look.
-(faint cheering)

22:44.571 --> 22:46.448
Look at your people.

22:46.531 --> 22:48.575
(cheering, applause)

22:51.828 --> 22:52.913
