-(indistinct chatter)

23:10.764 --> 23:12.474
-(applause)
-Jasmine.

23:12.557 --> 23:13.809
WOMAN:
You're my hero.

23:13.892 --> 23:16.144
(overlapping fan chatter)

23:16.228 --> 23:17.646
Thank you...

23:17.729 --> 23:19.272
(cheering, applause)

23:19.356 --> 23:21.566
(rhythmic applause)

23:25.737 --> 23:27.656
<i>"Invenibus...</i>

23:27.739 --> 23:30.033
<i>in aliis vero."</i>

23:30.117 --> 23:32.160
(cheering, rhythmic applause)

23:40.210 --> 23:42.212
Go home!

23:48.760 --> 23:50.804
(cheering, applause)

23:56.476 --> 23:58.520
-(rhythmic applause)
-Come on! Go, run!

24:05.569 --> 24:07.571
(applause continues)

24:26.798 --> 24:29.259
Holy shit, Jas,
what the hell was that?

24:29.342 --> 24:32.262
I'm telling you,
it's this frickin' coin.

24:32.345 --> 24:35.223
Okay, I can't believe
I'm even entertaining this idea,

24:35.307 --> 24:36.683
