24:49.321 --> 24:50.739
{\an8}She is the winner
of the world's

24:50.822 --> 24:52.699
{\an8}most famous
singing competition,<i> Ovation.</i>

24:52.782 --> 24:56.870
{\an8}Please welcome Jasmine Delancey!

24:56.953 --> 24:58.747
{\an8}(cheering, applause)

24:58.830 --> 25:00.916
{\an8}There she is!
(laughs)

