25:18.516 --> 25:20.101
-(applause continues)
-Oh, okay, all right.

25:20.185 --> 25:21.353
It is a <i> talk</i> show.

25:21.436 --> 25:24.105
-Right, right. (laughs)
-I think

25:24.189 --> 25:26.233
there might be a little bit
of talking.

25:26.316 --> 25:28.109
The-the first question
I have to ask you:

25:28.193 --> 25:31.529
What was the inspiration
for your famous song?

25:31.613 --> 25:34.324
Ah, you know,

25:34.407 --> 25:36.785
Fiji inspired "Fire Lady."

25:36.868 --> 25:39.579
I wouldn't be here
without her, you know?

25:39.663 --> 25:41.915
(cheering, applause)

25:41.998 --> 25:43.458
JASMINE:
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

25:43.541 --> 25:44.668
Yeah. No, Fiji was special.

25:44.751 --> 25:46.503
-She was... she really was.
-(cheering, applause continue)

25:46.586 --> 25:48.296
I think they're saying
<i>you're</i> special.

25:48.380 --> 25:50.590
This is...

25:50.674 --> 25:52.259
This isn't
every guest gets this, you know.

25:52.342 --> 25:55.178
These-these people love you.

25:55.262 --> 25:57.597
-Wow. Wow.
-JASMINE: Okay.

25:57.681 --> 25:58.932
Stop it, stop it. Stop it.

25:59.015 --> 26:00.475
Well, you know, I mean,

26:00.558 --> 26:02.143
