28:59.362 --> 29:02.157
(whispers):
I can't, Z, I can't.

29:02.240 --> 29:04.617
Why?

29:04.701 --> 29:06.453
I'm nothing without it.

29:06.536 --> 29:07.704
Are you kidding me?

29:07.787 --> 29:09.831
You're you.

29:09.914 --> 29:11.916
You always will be you.

29:16.588 --> 29:18.840
(Jasmine sniffles)

29:18.923 --> 29:20.967
(sighs)

29:22.135 --> 29:25.305
-Ah!
-And then you can just go.

29:25.388 --> 29:26.264
-Okay. Okay.
-Go to the lake house.

29:26.347 --> 29:30.602
